## Our Solution: Fostering Innovation and Inclusivity

This initiative strongly resonates with **Sustainable Development Goal 9 (Industry, Innovation, and Infrastructure)** by promoting inclusive and sustainable industrialisation and fostering innovation. By fully documenting this project and making it available on GitHub, we aim to create a culture of open-source innovation. This will allow others to adapt and improve upon the technology for various applications beyond agriculture.

This commitment to open access also aligns with **Sustainable Development Goal 4 (Quality Education)**. It allows people to learn from and use this technology for their own projects, granting them access to a greater range of microcontroller and screen applications, where the inability to display the Lao language may have previously been a significant barrier.

***
